boldJava window not opening from the browser/bold:

This happens due to security reasons. 
You can fix this by going to the Java control Panel (Control Panel> Search> Java control panel)
You may not see the Java control panel, if Java is not installed on your computer. 
Install Java: https://java.com/en/download/
Once Java is installed, you should see the Java Control panel  (Control Panel> Search> Java control panel)
Open Java Control Panel
Go to Advanced tab
Scroll down to see 'Advanced Security Settings'
Here, UNCHECK these 2 options
	-Use TLS 1.1
	-Use TLS 1.2